name: Rain City - NOIR Tee
description:
The city never sleeps and Rain City is no exception. After its older brother claimed urban stardom on the streets of Manchester, our flagship tee emerges again in it's darker form.

Here at Bakery Fresh we promote an active and original lifestyle, and after listening carefully to your feedback we are proud to present the Rain City NOIR Tee: for those who understand that the night can be just as exciting as the day.

Printed on Gildan SoftStyle tees


Size Guide:
Small 36/38
Medium 40/42
Large 44/46
XL 48/50

Model is wearing Medium

name: Rain City - ORIGINAL Tee
description:
We say "Love Your City", and so does this shirt in a weird kind of way. At Bakery Fresh, we are proud of our heritage and wouldn't trade the rainy streets of Manchester for any other. Printed on super soft white tees, our flagship shirt is perfect for skating, partying, exploring, relaxing, or just sleeping. 

Printed on Gildan SoftStyle tees
